{"tid":1657634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[是咁的]我係葉瘤，十月二十日請參加民陣大遊行","createTime":"2019-10-16T07:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T04:12:50.000Z","uid":136992,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"93fc6946c7def7049e2999f439f7535652b72e59","tid":1657634,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:36:40.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n各位好，我係葉瘤，呻吟黨主席。<br />\n係呢四個月，大家都好嬲妹妹同警察對市民的不公，暴力和選擇性執法。<br />\n在美國正式實施人權法之前，我想同美國講我一直推動政府維護港人自由自主，我勞碌奔波維護港人利益。<br />\n我建議妹妹成立獨立調查委員會，以法懲治黑警，亦會推動真普選。十月二十日我會同大家一齊參加民陣大遊行，聽下後生仔的意見。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n各位選民，希望大家繼續支持我，<br />\n各位美國政界大佬，請留意下我支持民主自由，我同我個囡都好需要美國簽證。<br />\n共享大灣區留返比妹妹。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十月二十民陣九龍大遊行</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xfBUKmQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxfBUKmQ.jpg&h=a5d52ddd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0065b0adef71fea82cf12e1a5ada3ce6d8bb18d6","tid":1657634,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgjbDGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgjbDGh.jpg&h=e5447ac9&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4da8c83d1a4741eb169844484b809ba32152d6fd","tid":1657634,"uid":136992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:44:25.000Z","msg":"十月二十民陣九龍大遊行"},{"pid":"c22f87f7653ce618bf639784d8ea2415af8df540","tid":1657634,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:52:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n